\id 2JN - Aneme Wake NT [aby] -Papua New Guinea 1988 (DBL -2013)
\h 2 Dioni
\toc1 DIONINU ABANARO OWAOWA
\toc2 2 Dioni
\toc3 2 Dion
\mt1 DIONINU ABANARO OWAOWA
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ae Godinu we mune odi aweka. Na i sosi yawokeka dai mima aini anu amara arumabake arie wake weada yewa owaowa yanake odakunea eawe. Naini Godinu ba wake iwoka sinaisa orouini iyanu imuka yaisina abairo ibinu.
\v 2 Enoya Godinu ba wake iyabairo ibinuba idua iyabairo ibene ibene ibeifeku enoba ibai imukada iyanu imuka yaisina abairo ibinu.
\p 
\v 3 Babae Godini Danu Amara Yesu Kerisoini emuama iyabake emenu irauaiai unu korekaini imukari ukekaini irauaiai ibekaini mafisiro ba wake mane wefeke iyanu iyanu imukari uke makafene ibake weakune.
\s1 Imukari ukekaini ba wake weeka
\p 
\v 4 Anu moi amara aruma Godinu ba wake naukada gienabu enaraisaro eme moima ibai eraada nabairo weaisaro na naukada rooro daiwere ukakune. Godima eno wei ibake anu amara aruma Godinu wake naukada enaraisaro na rooro daiwere ukakune.
\v 5 Enoba ae Godima we mune odiai aweka abake awoena darawadu wake owaowa yanake ode dakakune. Enoba yewa darawadu wake adinaroma iyabairo ma’iro ibinu. Ibake i darawadunu wake eno weaku, yanu yanu imukari uke makaewe weaku.
\v 6 Ya Godinu wake naukaisaie yanu yanu imukari uke makanaisa. Enoya yewa wake eaweke imukari uke makaewe weakune. Enoba Godima adinaro i demui wake iyabairo weiro iya nauisi.
\s1 Yesunu ba irau wake mamenewaa ufene wei wake
\p 
\v 7 We irukeka eme keuwere yewa orofaro enaada emuama eno weaisa, i Yesu Keriso Dawa ba eme sine dauia eno weaisa ibake i orou emuae we irukeka oroua weaisi.
\v 8 Enoba i orou emuae wasai kerisoya erenewaa uyakawe! I orounu ukaisa enaenari dauawero Godima yanu moko makeka da mareke mufia. I Godinu irau waiya mane ukenewaa uawero Godima yanu moko yaisina irauaiai mafia.
\p 
\v 9 Ainama Kerisonu wake naukenewaa uke dakaada nono danu imusu arara mane ukakuie dawa Godibairo ibe dakaku. Enoba ainama Yesunu ba wake naukenewaa ukaada enaenari ukakuie i ba Godini Danu Amaraini Emuae dawabairo ibinisi.
\v 10 Enoba ainama yabairo fafekuke Yesunu ba irau wake da wefekuke imusu we ma iwoka ufekuie yanu uwara ubarenaro amuaweke moko wake da weaweke arie wake da weawe.
\v 11 Nono ainama i mibake arie wake wefekuke we erakune danu uwararo anifekuie dawaini i mini i merama waiya demuiro ufisisi.
\s1 I dubuena kai wake
\p 
\v 12 Nanu wake keuwere abake wemane ukaadama nono na arara me owaowaro yanakeka ibake abairo famauro ba wakeroma wake wake we makafukuke aini naini rooro daiwere uke makafuku.
\p 
\v 13 Anu Godima we mune odi arumanu amara aruma emuama abairo arie wake we odaisaisa.
\p Nanu wake idua me sininu. 
